=============================================================================
 Marml - XHTML Rendering Made Better
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
 a.k.a. "Marml Ain't a Real Markup Language"
=============================================================================

Flexible, inventive alternative to ERB and other Ruby-driven templating
systems.

 * Clearly a work in progress. The master branch will contain a working
   prototype as soon as is practical.

